data.description: Charming brick ranch home, freshly painted and recently updated. Located  across the street from Smith Woods. This beautiful home offers  3 bedrooms , 2 baths  and a partially finished basement with 2 bonus rooms to use as you wish for extra bedrooms, in-law suite, workout room, office, etc., laundry room, family room, and a three-season room with 6 patio doors. Excellent location -  close to the Fairview train station; in Downers Grove North high school district 99 boundaries, Herrick junior high, and Whittier grade school. Truly move-in. Must see !
